quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,61,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sezifika izithunywa ebantwini baLothi
  15,62,Wathi “ngempela nina ningabantu abangaziwa”
  15,63,"Zathi, (izithunywa) “Qhabo size lapha kuwena nalokho abangabaza ngakho”"
  15,64,"Futhi size kuwena neqiniso, ngempela thina singabaneqiniso"
  15,65,Ngakho-ke hamba nomndeni wakho ngengxenye yobusuku futhi ubalandele ngemumva futhi kungabi khona ngisho noyedwa wenu ozobheka ngemumva futhi niye lapho eniphoqwe ukuya khona
  15,66,Futhi salwenza lwazeka kuyena lelo daba ukuthi izimpande zalaba (abayizoni) zizonqunywa ekuseni
  15,67,Futhi abantu bedolobha bafika begcwele injabulo
  15,68,"Wathi\t“ngempela\tlezi\tizihambeli\tzami\tngakho-ke ningangihlazi.”"
  15,69,Futhi sabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningangihlazi
  15,70,"Bathi\t(abantu\tbaLothi)\t“asizange\tyini\tsikwenqabele (ekungeniseni) abantu na?”"
  15,71,"Wathi\t(uLothi)\t“lawa\tngamadodakazi\tami\tuma\tnina ningabenzi (bokuhle).”"
  15,72,"(Isifungo)\tngempilo\tyakho!\tNgempela\tbona\tbadideke umqondo bayaphuphutheka njengezimpumputhe"
  15,73,Ngakho-ke bathathwa ukukhala (umsindo) owesabekayo ngesikhathi sokuphuma kwelanga
  15,74,Ngakho-ke (idolobha lase-Sodom) saligumbuqela phansi futhi sanethisa phezu kwabo amatshe obumba olugazingiwe
  15,75,Ngempela kulokhu kunezimpawu kulabo ababonayo
  15,76,Futhi ngempela lona (idolobha laseSodom) lalisemgaqweni omkhulu
  15,77,Ngempela kulokho kunophawu kubantu abakholwayo
  15,78,Futhi izihlali zasehlathini (abantu baseMidyan) ngempela babengalungile
  15,79,Ngakho-ke saziphindisela kubona futhi ngempela wona womabili (amadolobha) asemgaqweni osobala